<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Tasha Mellett Foundation Launch</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #c1e965;
        color: #000;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .section h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #c1e965;
      }

      .section p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #c1e965;
        color: #000 !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: 17px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #a9d64f;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f9fff2;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .social-links a {
        color: #c1e965;
        margin: 0 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .social-links a:hover {
        color: #a9d64f;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>The Tasha Mellett Foundation Is Officially Live</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h1>Hope. Kindness. Action.</h1>
        <p>
          We’re honored to share that the
          <strong>Tasha Mellett Foundation</strong> is now live. Our mission is
          to spread kindness, create opportunities, and support communities in
          need.
        </p>
        <p>
          From grassroots projects to impactful initiatives, this is the start
          of something that can truly change lives. And we’d love for you to be
          part of it.
        </p>
        <a class="cta-button" href="<%= frontendUrl %>" target="_blank">
          Join the Movement →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Stay connected</p>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/tashamellettfoundation">Instagram</a> |
          <a href="https://twitter.com/tashamellettfdn">Twitter</a> |
          <a href="https://facebook.com/tashamellettfoundation">Facebook</a>
        </div>
        <p>© 2025 Tasha Mellett Foundation. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
